description: If you miss the subtly sweet, spicy tobacco flavors pulling back from the tip of a classic American cigarette, Aqua’s American Red flavor is going to hit the spot.
Blue Razz by Aqua E-Liquid is a delicious sweet blue raspberry flavored E-Liquid that will tantalize your taste buds with each inhale!
Blue Razz by Aqua Salt E-Liquid is a deliciously sweet and slightly tart blue raspberry vape. This e liquid has a smooth and fruity flavor that will have you coming back for more.
Cyclone by Aqua E-Liquid Cream Collection is the famous early morning treat that everybody loves. A milky cereal that's so sweet it will blow your mind!
Flow by Aqua E-Liquid is a delicious tropical fruit combination of sweet pineapple with juicy mango and a hint of guava to balance the flavor. Clean, crisp, refreshing.
Ice Flow by Aqua E-Liquid is a delicious tropical fruit combination of sweet pineapple with juicy mango and a hint of guava with a kick of menthol. Clean, crisp, refreshing.

Flow by Aqua Salt E-Liquid is a tropical salt nicotine blend that tastes like paradise. The combination of tangy pineapple, sweet guava, and juicy mango is like an exotic beach vacation for your taste buds.
Glacier by Aqua Salt E-Liquid is a minty menthol made with high quality salt nicotine and sweet notes of fresh mint.

As one of Aqua’s sweet tobacco flavors, Gold is a layered flavor experience that leaves a tingle on the tip of your tongue. With the decadent flavor of French vanilla custard combine with a smooth tobacco blend, you should be vaping Aqua Gold right now.
Lush by Aqua E-Liquid Cream Collection is a delicious bar that is smothered in mouthwatering and tarty lemon cream.

Mist by Aqua E-Liquid is an extraordinary blend of summer-ripened fruits featuring prominent tones of green apple, juicy peach, and the exotic taste of kiwi. The inhale starts with a crisp coat of tart green apple notes backed by the notes of peach and kiwi undertone. The peach flavor becomes more prominent during the exhale as the kiwi twists around the green apple finish.

Ice Mist by Aqua E-Liquid is an extraordinary blend of summer-ripened fruits featuring prominent tones of green apple, juicy peach, and the exotic taste of kiwi. The inhale starts with a crisp coat of tart green apple and menthol notes backed by the notes of peach and kiwi undertone. The peach flavor becomes more prominent during the exhale as the kiwi twists around the green apple finish.

Mist by Aqua Salt E-Liquid is a thirst-quenching salt nicotine treat for those hot summer days. Mist vape juice is a blend of tart green apples, sweet peaches and tangy kiwis. Every hit unveils notes of sourness, sweetness and tropical fruit tang.
Momentum by Aqua E-Liquid is a tropical delicacy of delicious mouth watering mangoes. This tropical treat will have you in bliss with each puff, whilst leaving a trail of tantalizing aroma.
Momentum by Aqua E-Liquid is a tropical delicacy of delicious mouth watering mangoes. This tropical treat will have you in bliss with each puff, whilst leaving a trail of tantalizing aroma.

Momentum Ice by Aqua E-Liquid is a frozen tropical delicacy of delicious mouth watering mangoes. This tropical treat will have you in bliss with each puff, whilst leaving a cool trail of frozen wonder.

If you’re the type of vaper that likes the refreshing pick-me-up that your vape device provides, the New Menthol e-liquid from Aqua is exactly what you’re looking for. Put a little minty freshness into those clouds you’re chucking with a new, smooth menthol experience.

Aqua Salt E-Liquids Oasis is a calming yet exhilarating fruit salt nicotine blend that combines juicy peaches with crisp cantaloupe chunks and sweet papaya flavor. These fruits sing together in beautiful harmony as the juices rush to the back of the throat.

Oasis by Aqua E-Liquid is one of the most popular flavors from this line. Oasis has a flavor profile of three amazing tropical fruits; papaya, peach, and pineapple is one of the greatest flavors from this brand.
Ice Oasis by Aqua E-Liquid is one of the most popular flavors from this line. Oasis has a flavor profile of three amazing tropical fruits and menthol; papaya, peach, and pineapple.
Pure by Aqua E-Liquid is a sweet trifecta fruit mix of fresh strawberries, juicy watermelon, and sweet, yet tart apple.

One of the smoothest, most relaxing vape experiences on the market has got to be AQUA’s line of menthol nic salts. Just like a daiquiri at sundown, exhaling a big cloud of this subtle mixture of watermelon, apple, and strawberries is just what you needed.
Ice Pure by Aqua E-Liquid is a sweet trifecta fruit mix of fresh strawberries, juicy watermelon, and sweet, yet tart apple with a touch of menthol.

Aqua Salt Pure is a thirst-quenching fruit salt nic blend that's perfect for warm summer weather. The combination of sweet strawberries, crisp apples, and cool watermelon slices makes us think of the delicious fruits that ripen beneath the hot summer sun.
Rainbow Drops by Aqua Salt E-Liquids is a sugary and fruity salt nicotine flavor that tastes exactly like the rainbow. Rainbow Drops delivers a tart and sugary flavor extravaganza that hits the spot.

Rainbow Drops Ice by Aqua Salt E-Liquids is a iced and fruity salt nicotine flavor that tastes exactly like the rainbow. Rainbow Drops Ice delivers a tart, sugary flavor extravaganza that hits the spot on hot days.
Rush by Aqua E-Liquid is a full fledged candied blueberry fruit flavor infused with tart and sweet notes throughout the entire bottle. This e-juice is the perfect solution for any sweet tooth!

watermelon flavor is the perfect balance of sweet and sour.

Vortex by Aqua E-Liquid Cream Collection features an amazing mixture of tantalizing creamy vanilla custard with graham crackers. The sweet and aromatic vanilla custard harmonizes well with the cinnamon and honey flavor one can get from graham crackers, making this the perfect e-liquid for those dessert lovers.
Bam’s Birthday Cannoli is a delicious e-juice encasing vanilla frosting while generously rolled over colorful sprinkles and topped with whipped cream!
Bam’s Captain Cannoli is another cereal flavor rolled around in a vanilla cream filling and topped off with whipped cream. Cereal has never tasted so good!

Bam’s Original Cannoli is key lime filling rolled in a layer of your favorite fruity cereal, and topped off with a dollop of homemade whipped cream. All three tasty ingredients are perfectly balanced to make a sweet cereal dessert you’d never expect.
Bam's Strawberry Cannoli is a perfectly browned cannoli shell filled with a sweet and creamy fresh strawberry filling all that goodness dusted with powdered sugar to bring it all home.

It consists of a crisp lemon cookie that’s bursting with flavorful goodness, and slathered in a sticky and sweet raspberry jam that wakes up every single taste bud, giving you a reason to celebrate.

Smooth Banana Ice by Fruitia is a blend of ripe banana and smooth, frosty menthol for a frozen banana vape that you’ll want to chill out with all day long. Naturally sweet and deliciously cold, this is one banana flavor you won’t want to miss out on.

Smooth Banana Ice Salt from Fruitia Salts is a remarkably smooth, deliciously frosty banana vape in a satisfying high-nicotine formulation for your favorite low-power device. Chill out with this blend of naturally sweet banana and crisp menthol all day, every day.

Strawberry Coconut Refresher Salt by Fruitia is a high-nicotine salt e-liquid and in our opinion, the perfect summertime fruit vape. Creamy tropical coconut and ripe sliced strawberries mingle to make an ultra-refreshing eliquid that brings back memories of warm sand and cool beach breezes. Enjoy Strawberry Coconut Refresher Salt in your favorite low-powered vape kit to taste the flavors of vacation year-round.

Sweet Peach Soda by Fruitia takes the familiar flavor of a bubbly, sweet peach soda and transforms it into a refreshing vape. Give your taste buds a Southern treat with this crisp summery flavor that blends peach juice, white peach, and strawberry to make one delicious beverage-inspired vape.

Give yourself a taste of Southern hospitality with this crisp blend of sweet peach juice, white peach and strawberry that will keep you satisfied all day long.
